{"tid":310290,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友好悲觀 究竟有冇方法解決","createTime":"2017-07-05T16:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T10:45:27.000Z","uid":27161,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f21f112009cbaea04813fd21ec5e9e3866dd0a77","tid":310290,"uid":27161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:24:03.000Z","msg":"我女朋友平時會好正常<br />\n<br />\n就係成日夜晚會亂諗嘢<br />\n<br />\n點樣亂諗嘢？會發我脾氣話我冇關心佢發夢俾人姦<br />\n<br />\n會無啦啦喊(隔住個電話) 話我唔關心佢<br />\n<br />\n會同我講連登咁多人揾sp fwb, 我都一定會。。<br />\n<br />\n個個對感情都唔真實 每個人都為利益而拍拖<br />\n<br />\n其實我對佢好好 但而家份工好難覆佢訊息 <br />\n<br />\n但以前返學 每日都會搵佢傾計或者見面食飯 <br />\n<br />\n最奇怪係呢頭氹完佢 好開心好sweet 過左幾個鐘<br />\n<br />\n就會變返原本咁 鬧交嘅時候都毫不留情 會話我冇用<br />\n<br />\n咩說話都講得出。。真係好傷心<br />\n<br />\n同埋我同佢拍左拖1年半都無搞過佢 <br />\n<br />\n自問已經好尊重佢。。同埋自己忍得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab8538ef50c66ce0d72fd1009b91dd95c5b26b5","tid":310290,"uid":78572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:29:59.000Z","msg":"有冇考究過佢之前會唔會發生過d咩事令到佢咁?"},{"pid":"6abf20be683a216e05bc92ba77a08852909554d3","tid":310290,"uid":108238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"similar with mine<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf806dd5b8043ea2206e70d6f1c3cafec6750e4","tid":310290,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:39:28.000Z","msg":"有病睇醫生"},{"pid":"e876c2930a1ba6fb516572a4b8a858f0bdd85090","tid":310290,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"好老實講，幾愛佢都好，咁樣好難走得幾遠"},{"pid":"8173c091914a812554e4980fc58f575452268b70","tid":310290,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a55512b0fc252b25edf067922d2eec3c6563d7ca","tid":310290,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:43:22.000Z","ms